12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
14 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
15 A. There is hereby appropriated to the County Improvements for
16 Roads and Bridges Fund created pursuant to Section 507 of Title 69
17 of the Oklahoma Statutes from any monies not otherwise appropriated
18 from the General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for the fiscal
19 year ending June 30, 2026, the sum of Twenty-five Million Dollars
20 ($25,000,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary for the
21 reconstruction of county bridges on the portion of the county
22 highway system defined as Major Collector routes in accordance with
23 the provisions of Section 654 of Title 69 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
24 Projects proposed by the counties will be submitted to, evaluated,
